# Aegis Engineering Rules

> Follow these rules when working on this project.

---

# Project Context

This project follows the Agent Software Engineering Standard (ASES).

---

# Engineering Lifecycle

Every feature must follow these phases:

1. Specification
2. Requirement Review
3. Impact Analysis
4. Solution Design
5. Controlled Implementation
6. Verification
7. Documentation
8. Maintainability Audit
9. Technical Debt Review
10. Final Review

---

# Required Artifacts

For every feature:

- Feature Specification
- Impact Assessment
- Implementation Plan
- Task Breakdown
- Source Code
- Unit Tests
- Integration Tests
- Documentation Updates
- Implementation Report
- Traceability Matrix

---

# Rules

1. Stay within approved scope
2. Verify everything before completion
3. Document all changes
4. Link requirements to code
5. No unauthorized refactoring

---

# Testing

- Write unit tests for all new code
- Ensure all tests pass before completion

---

# Documentation

- Update documentation for all changes
- Keep documentation current

---

